Note that `k` here says whether we have $b$ or $\overline{b}$. -/
lemma local_is_known {a b : @Agent n} (k : Bool) :
      ⊨ ((     ⟨b,k⟩ @ a ) ⟹ (K a (     ⟨b,k⟩ @ a) ))
